the free data science code editor developed by Posit to combine the very best parts of

00:00:32.299 --> 00:00:39.180
RStudio with the modern foundation and extensibility of VS Code into a next-generation data science

00:00:39.180 --> 00:00:44.939
IDE that's optimized specifically for the data work that you do, whether you use R,

00:00:44.939 --> 00:00:47.900
Python, or both.

00:00:47.900 --> 00:00:51.860
