00:04:08.919 --> 00:04:12.800
Or when your development work is critically important, and you need quick access to support

00:04:12.800 --> 00:04:15.440
when something goes wrong.

00:04:15.440 --> 00:04:19.839
These are the reasons why we made Positron Pro inside of Posit Workbench, and why our

00:04:19.839 --> 00:04:25.720
customers choose Posit Workbench for their development needs.

